{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"果然是杀人的利器，果然不假。","tone":"感叹","chapter":28,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这个多尔甲却是假的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"你看得出？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这人的死，也是假的。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"这就连我也看得出来。","tone":"微笑","chapter":28,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"这种刀锋可以缩回去的魔刀，我已看过不止一次，却连一次都没有插过我。","tone":"微笑","chapter":28,"line_start":138,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"要骗过你，的确也不容易。","tone":"淡然","chapter":28,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"看来这次已不是假的。","tone":"感叹","chapter":28,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":null,"text":"他本不必来送死。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"他也不配你出手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我并没有出手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"看来上官小仙果然没有说错。","tone":"感叹","chapter":28,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她说什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"她说你是这世上最可怕的三个人其中之一，甚至就是最可怕的一个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":164,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她的确没有说错。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"你不必再要别人来送死了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":174,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"就是你。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"好！好眼力！你是怎么看出来的？","tone":"大笑","chapter":28,"line_start":188,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"你们的人可以作假，脚下的脚印是假不了的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"想不到你对本门的功夫，居然也很熟悉。","tone":"无奈","chapter":28,"line_start":200,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"天魔十三大法，在我眼里看来，根本不值一文。","tone":"淡然","chapter":28,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"好，很好。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":204,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"现在我已只剩一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你们有两个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"出手的却只有一个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":260,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你虽不出手，也已威胁到我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":262,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":264,"line_end":264},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为你的刀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":266,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"我的刀并不是用来暗算别人的。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"可是只要有刀在，就已威胁到我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":272,"line_end":272},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"你要我走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":274,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你也不能走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":276,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":278,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我们三个人既然都已来了，至少就得有两个人死在这里。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":280,"line_end":282},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"你杀了他，还要杀我？","tone":"调侃","chapter":28,"line_start":284,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"所以你不能走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"难道你要我先交出我的刀，然后坐在这里等死？","tone":"调侃","chapter":28,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我只要你答应一件事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":290,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"你说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":292,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你已说过，你们绝不会两个人同时出手。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你说的话我相信，你并不是言而无信的小人。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":298,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"多谢。","tone":"微笑","chapter":28,"line_start":300,"line_end":300}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"所以他活着时，你的刀就绝不能出手。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"他若死了呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只要看见我一招得手，就可以发你的刀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":306,"line_end":306},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"怎么样才叫做一招得手？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只要我的手已打在他身上，就叫做一招得手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"只要你的手打在他身上，他就已必死无疑？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我的手本就是武器，能一招杀人的才能算做武器。","tone":"得意","chapter":28,"line_start":314,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"现在我明白了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你答应？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":320,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"我答应，因为我欠你的情。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":322,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你几时欠了我的情？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"那次的事我既然没有忘记，你当然也不会忘记。","tone":"微笑","chapter":28,"line_start":328,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我并不欠你的。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"所以你这次若杀了我，我绝不怪你。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"很好，这句话我的确绝不会忘记。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":336,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"只不过第一个要死的还是你。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":28,"line_start":338,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"你好像还是忘记了一件事。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"我若没有把握杀你，怎么会特地约你来？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"也许你本来的确有几分把握，只可惜你也忘记了一件事。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":348,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"你不该泄露了你的秘密。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"什么秘密？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":356,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"杀人的秘密。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":358,"line_end":358},{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"你不该用这种法子杀他的，你本该留着这一招来对付我。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":362,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_duo_er_jia","text":"我不用这法子，也一样可以杀你。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":366,"line_end":366}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":530,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_duo_er_jia","speaker_name":"多尔甲","listener":null,"text":"你……","tone":"痛苦","chapter":28,"line_start":454,"line_end":456},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"多尔甲（内心）","listener":null,"text":"你虽然杀了我，毁灭了我这个人，却还是没有毁灭我这双手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"多尔甲（内心）","listener":null,"text":"我这双手还是天下无双的武器。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你不想揭开他的面具来看看？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"不必。","tone":"无奈","chapter":28,"line_start":490,"line_end":490},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你已知道他是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":492,"line_end":492},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"我认得这双手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":494,"line_end":494},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"这的确是天下无双的武器。","tone":"感叹","chapter":28,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只可惜无论多可怕的武器，本身都不能杀人的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":28,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"一件武器是否可怕，主要得看它是在什么人手里。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我那一招若是出手重了些，我的手很可能被他毁了。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":512,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"很可能。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"可是我那一招出手够轻，这就是胜负的关键。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":516,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"那一招的确妙得很。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":28,"line_start":518,"line_end":518},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"高手相斗，胜负的关键，往往就在一招间。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":520,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你既然已知道他是什么人，现在又想再看看他了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":524,"line_end":524},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_mo_jiu_xing","speaker_name":"墨九星","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"死人并没有什么好看的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_mo_jiu_xing","text":"但我却想看看，他临死前是不是也已明白这道理。","tone":"认真","chapter":28,"line_start":530,"line_end":530}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
